== logout in a non-login shell is refused:
shit: 1:1: error: Builtin 'logout': logout: not login shell: use exit.
     1 |  logout
       |  ^~~~~~ here.
rc=1
== logout with a non-numeric operand is a located error:
shit: 1:1: error: Builtin 'logout': logout: not login shell: use exit.
     1 |  logout abc
       |  ^~~~~~~~~~ here.
rc=1
